poLH2wGYRXLlXxUWuPvspmjDrceDh2DFT53BKO3w&oe=67011910"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills-IT_Screenshot-4_2560x1440px.png", "id": "466990229364879", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974719_466990232698212_429966222944110534_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=0uqF16y1cXUQ7kNvgEb69Mf&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDGpbN3HVRHrbeplnLXYSik0O9Mo7ThUKQuQiBcIG4uGw&oe=67012889"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills-IT_Screenshot-5_2560x1440px.png", "id": "1025636505558868", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982727_1025636508892201_430688725369663184_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=azF949fXAbwQ7kNvgHGBl5f&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBZTvvVs4tLSICrLMSxQ_6TscdYF87YmcfoKN0HchXqJw&oe=67012091"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-Landscape_2560x1440px.png", "id": "1630730634427910", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982566_1630730637761243_9068074757253837847_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=oErJp1KLJ5QQ7kNvgGXmVLL&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAE0mDVRAyyTkLZK88CmDUaSGnkzV_2XZ-UdFwcu3A9Lg&oe=67012DF3"}, "display_name": "Simulador Soft Skills", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Trasforma il tuo potenziale e distinguiti nella tua carriera!\nScopri il simulatore pensato per migliorare le tue \"Soft Skills\" attraverso diverse capsule formative essenziali con le quali potrai:\n\n1\ufe0f\u20e3 Autovaluta le tue competenze trasversali che ti aiuteranno ad adattarti a diversi ambienti lavorativi.\n2\ufe0f\u20e3 Difendi un discorso davanti a un pubblico per migliorare la tua comunicazione e parlare in pubblico.\n3\ufe0f\u20e3 Allena i tuoi punti di forza in un discorso commerciale.\n4\ufe0f\u20e3 Prendi decisioni per sviluppare le tue capacit\u00e0 strategiche e analitiche.\n5\ufe0f\u20e3 Lavorare in squadra per promuovere la collaborazione e l'efficienza del gruppo.\n6\ufe0f\u20e3 Preparati a svolgere con successo un colloquio di lavoro.", "short_description": "Potenzia le tue \"Soft Skills\" con il nostro simulatore di realt\u00e0 virtuale! Ideale per i professionisti che desiderano migliorare le proprie competenze interpersonali in modo immersivo e interattivo."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "SoftSkills_Logo_8100x1296px.png", "id": "1158856758691457", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974786_1158856762024790_8351105602424236604_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=-_-gx72y2EgQ7kNvgETGYpc&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDNFuTzLLyNOh80k0BDrhxhDxoexSAzy7hbgmzXw8f7KA&oe=670125E9"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-portrait_1008x1440px.png", "id": "1001238441075007", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031591_1001238447741673_2783185145492224256_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Q4nIlyv9JKIQ7kNvgFPkOkX&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDchx4cM-88zxUU1DD42_J4IJ92WBF-oOC1-GCoGHcN6A&oe=67013EAF"}, {"file_name": "INVELON_Icon-512x512px.png", "id": "837105901661785", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75476759_837105904995118_1711704673161247418_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=UA3T7YJw4IgQ7kNvgGkU1fJ&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA4empsgSyllsqYQ5bBMJZngXlIsZeLne_nPGyOfP_peg&oe=670133F3"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Hero-cover_3000x900px.png", "id": "436545955954692", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974777_436545959288025_6494250809818469750_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=v8UJtYfKp8QQ7kNvgHlS1nk&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCHIyTOdVYRmXcjuSp-1UXlEzgknOiiYX6jqy6x0w9JDw&oe=67011BC5"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-minilandscape_1080x360px.png", "id": "396479036730805", "image_type":