rtalezas en un discurso comercial.\n4\ufe0f\u20e3 Tomar decisiones para desarrollar tus habilidades estrat\u00e9gicas y anal\u00edticas.\n5\ufe0f\u20e3 Trabajar en equipo para fomentar la colaboraci\u00f3n y la eficiencia del grupo.\n6\ufe0f\u20e3 Prepararte para llevar a cabo con \u00e9xito una entrevista de trabajo.", "short_description": "\u00a1Impulsa tus \"Soft Skills\" con nuestro Simulador de Realidad Virtual! Ideal para profesionales que buscan mejorar sus habilidades interpersonales de forma inmersiva, interactiva y efectiva."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Softskills_Cover-Landscape-Padding.png", "id": "3682144288704654", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57570314_3682144292037987_5131369632409068623_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ZU0zS5WBtIQQ7kNvgFL6nfu&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYArh_cAmA_mDfWOI6JaQ3ovSrUyE1V_kKSIMw3fmt6dWQ&oe=6701147A"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Logo_8100x1296px.png", "id": "1994020534333698", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974910_1994020537667031_8688105079957652849_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ss4CjKKFjD0Q7kNvgG5FoZD&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCyB4VteWuwSPDVumKGnkuePqmvatBO1Y_cU9oUJ0JYWg&oe=67013443"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-square_1440x1440px.png", "id": "1247184912914732", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035311_1247184916248065_2567077078745571082_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1RdXibchD5cQ7kNvgHJCewZ&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAilxJo379HVgDKPtnqWvGtmsMPRcfN7E9mytTvQXcGwg&oe=67014273"}, {"file_name": "INVELON_Icon-512x512px.png", "id": "1187254515612530", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974888_1187254518945863_7395065576696775988_n.png?_nc_cat=1